export let SetUsersActionCreator = (users) =>
{
  return{
type:SET_USERS, users
  }
}

{

let ProfilesReducer = (state = initialState, action) =>
{
switch(action.type)
{
  case SET_USERS:
    {
      return{
        ...state,
        PrInf:[...state.PrInf,
               ...action.users]
      }
    }
}

return state
}
export default ProfilesReducer
